ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectWithdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in the Northwest Territories (Salt River First Nation) Order
PrecisOrder repealing P.C. 2006-547 and making of the Withdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in the Northwest Territories (Salt River First Nation) Order, which provides for the withdrawal from disposal, until August 31, 2009 of approximately 135.37 square kilometers of land to facilitate the addition to the Salt River Reserve in the Northwest Territories.
